FROM title t, cast_info ci, movie_keyword mk
WHERE t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year  <  2013 AND ci.person_id  >  3011416 AND ci.role_id  >  9 AND mk.keyword_id  =  7365
